= module Gtk::PrintOperationPreview

== Included Modules
* GLib::Interface

== Instance Methods
--- end_preview
     Ends a preview.

--- render_page(page_numer)
     Renders a page to the preview.
     * page_number: the page to render

--- selected?(page_number)
     Returns whether the given page is included in the set of pages that
     have been selected for printing.

     * page_number: a page number
     * Returns: true if the page has been selected for printing

== Signals
--- got-page-size: self, context, page_setup
     * self: a Gtk::PrintOperationPreview
     * context: a Gtk::PrintContext
     * page_setup: a Gtk::PageSetup

--- ready: self, context
     * self: a Gtk::PrintOperationPreview
     * context: a Gtk::PrintContext

